title: After School Dice Club
subTitle: Shy Miki and new student Aya discover classmate Midori works at a board game shop, leading the three girls to bond over their shared love of board games.

title: Blade Runner 2049
subTitle: K, an officer with the Los Angeles Police Department, unearths a secret that could create chaos. He goes in search of a former Blade Runner who has been missing for over three decades.

title: Hitch
subTitle: A professional dating expert helps men woo the women of their dreams. However, while helping a hapless client, he finds himself challenged by a gossip columnist.

title: Bad Boys II
subTitle: Mike and Marcus, the Miami Police Department detectives, investigate the flow of drugs into Miami. Their search leads them to a dangerous drug lord who is planning to control the city's drug trade.

title: Baby Driver
subTitle: When talented getaway driver Baby meets his dream girl, Debora, he chooses to leave his shady life behind. But when he is called in for one last heist with an unstable crew, things get dicey.

title: Lake Placid: The Final Chapter
subTitle: Reba builds an electric fence to block all the crocodiles in Black Lake. But when the fence is unknowingly left open, some students trespass on the property, which puts their lives in danger.

title: Daddio
subTitle: A woman takes a cab ride back home from the airport. En route, she unexpectedly has an insightful conversation with the driver regarding the important relationships in life.

title: The Equalizer 3
subTitle: As Robert McCall finds himself forming a new bond with the locals of an Italian town, the region's oppression by the Mafia triggers him to protect his people.

title: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
subTitle: Eddie Brock tries to revive his failing career by interviewing a serial killer, Cletus Kasady, who is on death row. When Carnage gains control over Cletus's body, he escapes from the prison.

title: Inferno
subTitle: After waking up with amnesia in a hospital, Robert Langdon teams up with Sienna Brooks, one of his doctors, to protect the world from the evil plan of a scientist.

title: The Adventures of Tintin
subTitle: Tintin's new model ship sparks an adventure of intrigue and theft. He uncovers a historical mystery involving treasure, rival groups and a quest for scrolls revealing a sunken ship's location.

title: Kill 'Em All 2
subTitle: Partnered by the CIA, Phillip and Vanessa return to Europe, facing a vengeful Russian-French terrorist Vlad, who wants to settle the score for his dead brother.

subTitle: Agent J of the Men in Black goes back in time to prevent the assassination of his partner, Agent K, at the hands of an alien criminal named Boris the Animal.

Jackson Curtis, a discontented writer, battles against all odds to keep his family secure when a series of apocalyptic calamities threaten to decimate humankind.
